                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">最喜：从前种种，譬如昨日死；从后种种，譬如今日生；此义理再生之身也。... ... 务要日日知非，日日改过；一日不知非，即一日安于自是；一日无过可改，即一日无步可进；天下聪明俊秀不少，所以德不加修、业不加广者，只为因循二字，耽搁一生。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="439977926">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-439977926" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-439977926" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="439977926">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/titilin/">小K童鞋</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-09-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">时下世风日下，人心不古，此文应该好好读读，须知积善之家，必有余庆。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

